{{Campaignbox Hussite Wars}}

The '''Battle of Nebovidy''' was fought on January 6, 1422 between the [[Holy Roman Empire]] and the [[Hussite]]s.  The Hussites were led by [[Jan Žižka]], while the Imperial forces were led by [[Sigismund, Holy Roman Emperor|Emperor Sigismund]].  The Hussites were victorious. {{coord missing|Czech Republic}}

