{{Infobox flag
| Name = Bago Region
| Image = Flag of Bago Division.svg
| Symbol = {{FIAV|normal}}
| Proportion = 2:3
| Adoption =
| Design = A blue flag with a yellow [[Hamsa (bird)|hamsa]] in the centre and "Bago Division" written in Burmese underneath it
