The '''[[Kosovo]]{{ref label|status|a|}} Identity Card''' is an ID card issued to the citizens of Kosovo for the purpose of establishing their identity, as well as serving as proof of residency, right to work and right to public benefits.<ref>[http://www.assembly-kosova.org/common/docs/ligjet/2008_3-L099_al.pdf "The Law on the ID Cards"] ''kuvendikosoves.org''. Accessed July 13, 2009.</ref>

