{{Infobox Bilateral relations|Kosovan–Lithuanian|Kosovo|Lithuania}}

'''Kosovan–Lithuanian relations''' involve foreign relations between [[Kosovo]]{{ref label|status|a|}} and [[Lithuania]]. [[Kosovo]] [[2008 Kosovo declaration of independence|declared its independence]] from [[Serbia]] on 17 February 2008 and Lithuania [[International reaction to the 2008 Kosovo declaration of independence|recognized]] it on 6 May 2008.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www3.lrs.lt/pls/INTER/w5_show?p_r=4445&p_d=76728&p_k=1|title=Seimas nutarė pripažinti Kosovo Respublikos nepriklausomybę (Seimas recognizes Republic of Kosovo's independence)|work=Parliament (Seimas) official proceedings|date=2008-05-06|accessdate=2008-05-06 |language=Lithuanian}}</ref> Diplomatic relations commenced on 16 July 2008.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://lrt.lt/news.php?strid=5042&id=4698767 |language=Lithuanian |title=Vyriausybė užmegs diplomatinius santykius su Kosovu |work=lrt.lt |publisher=Lietuvos nacionalinis radijas ir televizija. (Lithuanian national radio and television) |location=[[Vilnius]], [[Lithuania]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080916192423/http://www.lrt.lt/news.php?strid=5042 |archivedate=2008-09-16 |df= }}</ref>

==Military==

{{As of |2009}} Lithuania had 36 troops serving in Kosovo as peacekeepers in the [[NATO]]-led [[Kosovo Force]].<ref>[http://www.nato.int/kfor/structur/nations/placemap/kfor_placemat.pdf "Kosovo Force (KFOR)"] www.nato.int Link accessed 21-07-09
</ref> On November 30, 2009 Lithuania and Kosovo signed a military agreement to increase the breakaway region's integration into NATO and to bolster its disputed independence.<ref>
[http://balticreports.com/?p=5583 "Lithuania, Kosovo sign military agreement"] www.balticreports.com Link accessed 2009-11-30</ref>

On 30 November 2009 Kosovo and Lithuania strengthened military ties when their defence ministers met during a three-day visit to Lithuania.<ref>[http://www.newkosovareport.com/200911302119/Politics/Kosovo-and-Lithuania-strengthen-military-ties.html "Kosovo and Lithuania strengthen military ties"] 30-11-09 Link retrieved 03-12-09
</ref>

