{{main|Kebab}} {{more citations needed|date=August 2014}} [[File:Eggplant kebab and isot.jpg|thumb|Patlıcan kebabı is an eggplant kebab|320px]]
This is a list of [[kebab]] dishes from around the world. Kebabs are various cooked meat dishes, with their origins in [[Middle Eastern cuisine]] and the [[Muslim world]]. Although kebabs are often cooked on a [[skewer]], many types of kebab are not.<ref name="Ozlem's Turkish Table"> {{cite web | url=http://ozlemsturkishtable.com/2015/05/eggplant-kebab-with-yoghurt-marinated-chicken-patlicanli-kebap/ | title=Eggplant kebab with yoghurt marinated chicken; Patlicanli Kebap | author= Ozlem Warren | date=May 11, 2015 | website=Ozlem's Turkish Table | accessdate=February 24, 2016 }} </ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=gFK_yx7Ps7cC&pg=PT597 |title=Encyclopedia of Jewish Food|publisher=|accessdate=2 November 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=caBlQu0YwC4C&pg=PA30 |title=Punjabi Khana|publisher=|accessdate=2 November 2014}}</ref>
